travelplanapp.travelplanapp

Class PlanWorker

  • java.lang.Object
    • travelplanapp.travelplanapp.PlanWorker

  • @Path(value="/planworker")
public class PlanWorker
extends java.lang.Object
    PlanWorker is a class in charge of implementing tasks related to Trip plans. The methods in this class consume HTTP POST requests from task dispatcher and add/delete plans by adding/deleting entities in datastore.
